subject: Swimming
Pan Pacific Swimming Championships
lead_paragraph: Despite a younger and deeper field of competitors, the result of the 100-meter butterfly at the Pan Pacific Swimming Championships was familiar with Michael Phelps, 29, and Ryan Lochte, 30, taking the top two spots.
